{"tid":2010670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位對唔住，頭先我係同個手足鬥黃","createTime":"2020-05-10T14:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T14:28:03.000Z","uid":289605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dffe875aea53ed27707649a8e3a9cdd3c80c8198","tid":2010670,"uid":289605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pd8t2x7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpd8t2x7.png&h=f8adb76c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODfHnx7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODfHnx7.png&h=e2833ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Awdt2x8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwdt2x8.png&h=27e8dd9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢已經好耐無覆機，唔知係學緊打字定真係嬲咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我相信佢一定係手足嚟，只係有少少似龍心同劉馬車，手足智商有問題我都好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講番正經事，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該以後見到嚟種智商有問題嘅手足<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">五毛</span></span>，一係唔好理佢，一係好似我咁關心佢</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地成日同佢互屌做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我玩9佢果時有成十個回覆，成日洗板洗到咩都討論唔到，大家一齊以後都唔好覆佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3e37afbdceaceb32784c28b492415fa0b33fd0","tid":2010670,"uid":21319,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"自己搞掂啦"}]}